# Technology Stack Guidelines

The project uses:
- Next.js as the main framework
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- shadcn/ui for UI components
- InstantDB for data layer

When working with these technologies:
- Follow Next.js App Router patterns and conventions
- Use Tailwind CSS directly in components
- Implement shadcn/ui following their installation guide
- Use InstantDB for all data operations
